{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act24side_level_act24side_06_end","storyGroup":"act24side","storySort":12,"storyDependence":"act24side_level_act24side_06_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"CF-6","storyName":"禁飞区","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"夜刀与随从艾露猫各自表明了对火龙的态度，而老猎人却突然大为愤怒，将猎矛对准了夜刀......","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act24side/level_act24side_06_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act24side_06","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":10,"next":12,"characters":["夜刀","柏生义冈","随从艾露猫","工匠猫"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":2},{"type":"character","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fd/Avg_bg_36_g5_redleaflake.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"1","text":"","id":8},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#4$1","fadetime":"1.5","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"2","text":"","id":10},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"黑角干员，收到请回答，黑角。","id":11},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"......联系不上，信号太差了。","id":12},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"柏生先生......","id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"我执行任务的时候不喜欢带着累赘，要是跟不上前进的速度，麻烦您留在原地，或者原路返回营地。","id":14},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1","id":15},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"蠢货，我没想要和你们同行。","id":16,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/08/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"只要您要去找火龙，就请不要擅自离开我的身边，我必须确保您的安全。","id":18},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#6$1","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"你——","id":20,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#3$1","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"随从艾露猫，你继续说。","id":22},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":23},{"type":"playsound","key":"$MH_nekolow","id":24},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"喵，是这样的。","id":25,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"老夫追随的“猎人”接到了某位王室成员的委托，似乎是对方心情不好想要火龙的红玉做首饰，这才委托我们去寻找火龙的。","id":26,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"心情不好......你们那里讨伐火龙的理由都是这么随意的吗？","id":28},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"......那位委托人应该算是个例喵。","id":30,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"言归正传，老夫在靠近火山的森林里发现了这条火龙。","id":32,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"正想要追上去的时候突然被一股奇怪的力量卷了进去，等到反应过来就已经到这里了。","id":33,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"你记得是什么样的力量吗？","id":35},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":36},{"type":"playsound","key":"$MH_nekolow","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"完全没有印象了......喵。","id":38,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/34/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"能把火龙这样的生物带过来，这种力量也应当视作威胁，不过当下的情况......暂且搁置吧，你继续讲。","id":40},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"老夫初来时由于不熟悉环境，便一直尾随火龙，暗中观察着火龙的行为......喵。","id":42,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"据老夫的观察，火龙的异常是从它自己找到一个洞口，下去里面之后开始出现的。","id":43,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"洞口？是通往山体内部的吗？","id":45},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"是的喵。","id":47,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"你记得那里有什么特征吗？","id":49},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":50},{"type":"playsound","key":"$MH_nekolow","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"遗憾喵，简单看下去只是普通的洞穴罢了，火龙确实是在进入那里之后开始出现异常的。","id":52,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"老夫也曾进去探查过喵，但下面......","id":53,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"纵横交错的洞窟尤为复杂，几次尝试都没能找到火龙的位置喵。","id":54,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"老夫猜测火龙是在洞窟内占据了一个区域筑巢，应该是一片距离洞口比较近的宽阔空间喵。","id":55,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"根据露华村后洞穴中的情形来看，那个洞穴很可能和山里的这些洞窟相连。难怪火龙会出现在那里。","id":57},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"我还有件事情想要了解......你也见到了，我们之前与火龙的战斗并不轻松，事实上......很艰难。","id":59},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"至今我们尚不能对它造成有效的伤害，我对再次面对火龙很难保持乐观，预计要付出相当大的代价。","id":61},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"理解喵。","id":63,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"我想问的是，凭你对火龙的了解，我们下次想要战胜它，有几成的把握？","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"或者说，有没有什么办法可以提高我们获胜的可能性？","id":66},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":67},{"type":"playsound","key":"$MH_nekolow","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"很难判断喵......和正常的火龙相比，这头过于焦躁了，受到些许刺激就会展现出强烈的攻击欲望。","id":69,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/76/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"之前，老夫发现它的感官敏锐度也有了提升，直接导致了攻击方式的改变，这就是老夫说的异常所在......喵。","id":70,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/76/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#6$1","focus":"2","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"阁下与老夫的装备里都没有闪光球，也没有麻痹陷阱喵，老夫想不到什么可以困住火龙的办法。","id":72,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#6$1","focus":"1","id":73},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"所以可能性不大......是吗？","id":74},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"喵，要提升对火龙的伤害，老夫还是有些想法的，老夫观察到......阁下是否对双剑的使用方法缺少了解？","id":76,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"双剑......你是说这对奇怪的武器吗？确实在使用时，我有力不从心的感觉。","id":78},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"阁下手中的这对双剑，一定是来自我们那里的武器，且其品质极为优良，可以肯定是出自顶尖的工匠之手......喵。","id":80,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"咦......","id":82},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_751_1#4$1","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"工匠猫","text":"喵？","id":84,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/ff/Avg_avg_npc_751_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"双剑有一套专门的使用法门，老夫会精简地讲与你听。若是能够正确使用它，对火龙的伤害可以显著提升，但......","id":86,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"但？","id":88},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"一路前行至今，老夫见到了火龙在此地的处境，这让老夫有所思考......真的有必要讨伐火龙吗？","id":90,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/76/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"你的意思是不应该置火龙于死地吗？","id":92},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":93},{"type":"playsound","key":"$MH_nekolow","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"老夫认为，拥有强大武力的“猎人”通常是平衡生态的关键存在喵，狩猎行为会影响当地的生态，应当深思熟虑才行。","id":95,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/76/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"根据迄今的观察，火龙的活动范围距离村庄较远，它的活动不会危害村庄，况且......此地的生态似乎难称得上健康。","id":96,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/76/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"草食生物明显繁衍过度，对森林植被的破坏显而易见，火龙能够遏制草食生物的族群扩张，对环境并非无益......喵。","id":98,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"如果是在老夫那里，能够取得委托中需求的素材的情况下，老夫不会选择与无害的怪物为敌。","id":100,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/76/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"我的任务也并不是讨伐火龙，而是处理另一种致命的威胁——矿石病，只是目前与之相关的线索指向了火龙。","id":102},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"只要能查清矿石病的源头，杜绝其对村庄的威胁，这头怪物的命运就与我的任务无关。","id":104},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"你们......","id":106,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/08/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"为了弄清楚原因，我们必须......","id":108},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1","id":109},{"type":"stopmusic","id":110},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"你们！","id":112,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#3$1","focus":"2","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"猎人阁下？","id":114,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/83/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","name2":"avg_npc_750_1#3$1","focus":"1","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"不用管他。","id":116},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1","id":117},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"都是......都是你们害的！","id":118,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"你......","id":120},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_nervous_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":121,"musicid":1},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#6$1","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"（举起狩猎矛）","id":123,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"该死的！都怪你们！","id":124,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"柏生先生，你这是要做什么？","id":126},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#6$1","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"为什么？为什么你们就是不肯听我的话？","id":128,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"为什么啊？你们......你们非得不要命地闯入森林，像一群听不懂人话的畜生一样四处乱窜。","id":129,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"瞧瞧你们的样子，明明在那怪物面前毫无还手之力，却一定要妨碍我、阻挡我，追着我的猎物，还总是说着自己要保护什么......","id":130,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"事实是，就是因为你们不听我话，那个男娃现在还下落不明，那头该死的怪物还活得好好的！","id":132,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#4$1","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"我们在寻找能够对付火龙的办法，前期的失败是正常的。","id":134},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#6$1","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"你懂什么？只有你们这样的废物才会说做不到！","id":136,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"现在你们又说不应当讨伐火龙，以什么莫名其妙的懦弱理由......下一步你们就要救下我的猎物了是吗？","id":137,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#10$1","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"我明白了......你们就是来故意折磨我的吧？折磨我这个离死不远的老家伙......","id":139,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/75/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#6$1","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"就因为我还记得他！记得那些你们非要遗忘的事！所以你们就要用这种手段折磨我......","id":141,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"就像对他一样！剥下我的皮，放尽我的血，敲断我的肋骨，剖开我的胸口，抽出我的骨髓......","id":142,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"你......你说啊！","id":144,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#4$1","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"对不起，我完全无法理解你在说什么。","id":146},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"放下武器，我们继续前进，现在的情况容不得闲话了。","id":147},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"别动！","id":149,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#4$1","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"你能做什么？","id":151},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#6$1","id":152},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"你们给我滚，滚回你们来的地方！","id":153,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"我命令你们！滚啊！","id":154,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#3$1","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"不可能。","id":156},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#4$1","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"我再强调一遍，我没理由听从你的命令。","id":158},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"*东国粗口*为什么？为什么又是这样？","id":160,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#6$1","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"劝告的话一句都听不进去......保护别人？","id":162,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"凭什么？自以为是的白痴！只会把自己的意愿强加给别人吗？","id":164,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#4$1","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"......","id":166},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"没有人需要你们的保护！自己的选择就该自己承担！结局也都是自找的！","id":168,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#1$1","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"其他人就少管闲事！就应该*东国粗口*好好看着！","id":170,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/08/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"解决掉那头怪物......只能由我一个人去做，只有我配得上......","id":171,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/08/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#6$1","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"如果......你胆敢再往前一步，我就让你首先尝尝那种滋味！","id":173,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#3$1","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"不，你不会的。","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"你没有勇气。","id":176},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#6$1","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"停下！","id":178,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#4$1","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"你说的话对我来说意义不大......这柄狩猎矛......在你手中我也很难将其视作威胁。","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"就像我现在亦在步步向你靠近，而你的矛仍纹丝不动。","id":181},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1","id":182},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"我警告你！","id":184,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#3$1","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"放弃吧，你做不到。","id":186},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#4$1","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"既然你非要耽误时间，那我就与你说个清楚，断绝你后续的干扰。","id":188},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#6$1","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"什......停下！","id":190,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#4$1","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"要是你真的是这种想法，在屋子里你就能趁我们受伤处理掉我和黑角，满足你独享猎物的心愿，但你没有这么做。","id":192},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"不要再前进了......你！","id":194,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#4$1","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"或许我可以理解为你不愿意对同类痛下狠手，然而自始至终你的所有行为只是在劝离我们，我感受得到。","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"甚至不久前面对火龙时，你拦下我的方式是将我推离战场......你实际上不想我们遭受危险。","id":197},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1","id":198},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"胡说！","id":200,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"停下！我再说最后一次！","id":201,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#4$1","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"再回到狩猎，身为猎人，尽量以最少的代价解决猎物的威胁不是最优先的选择吗？","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"你们与残酷的大自然争斗那么久，怎么可能没有这样的判断。","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"你一直拒绝我们共同狩猎的要求，不顾战力差距执意独自面对猎物，置村庄的安危于不顾，这又明显与你试图保护我们的行为相冲突。","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"我有一个猜测，或许你讨伐火龙的行为纯粹出自你个人的执念。","id":206},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1","id":207},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"住嘴！","id":209,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#3$1","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"看你的表情，我应该没有猜错。","id":211},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"那我可以确认了，你的所作所为并不是出于对狩猎的渴望，你不过是被愤怒与悔恨驱使，盲目地追逐火龙。","id":213},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#10$1","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"但，那仅仅是你的自私而已......","id":215},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#4$1","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"现在的你，根本算不上什么猎人。","id":217},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#6$1","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"那......那就是我的猎物！你又不是猎人，有什么资格评判猎人？","id":219,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"停下！你停下！","id":221,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#4$1","id":222},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"如果你要否认我说的一切，那就请你对准我射出手中的武器，一切就如你所愿了。","id":223},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#3$1","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"我走到了这里，就在这里，在你的面前。","id":225},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#4$1","id":226},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"来啊。","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"杀了我啊。","id":228},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1","id":229},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"我！","id":230,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#6$1","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"我——","id":232,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#5$1","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"我......","id":234,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#4$1","id":235},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"柏生先生，到底是什么让你如此执着？","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"是柏生明吗？","id":237},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#5$1","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"你......你从哪里知道这个名字的？","id":239,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"我猜，他已经不在这个村庄里了，是吗？","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"他和你什么关系？姓氏相同，不会只是朋友。从照片来看，他比你和村长都要年轻，也曾经是个猎人，你拿的狩猎矛上就有他的名字。","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"或者，他是你的家人？","id":243},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#5$1","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"不要再说了......","id":245,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"你之前就不停地用“你们”这个称呼，我和他在你眼里有什么相似的地方吗？","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"我猜......过去他为了狩猎不顾你的意见，造成了不可挽回的后果，也因此离你而去......","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"你开始后悔，被痛苦纠缠......只能在狩猎中发泄情绪......","id":249},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"闭嘴！你根本......根本不理解......","id":251,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#3$1","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"我能理解。","id":253},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#12$1","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"陷入过去的滋味不好受，但这种情感只会让你做出错误的判断。你的执念并不能改变过去，只会让你停滞不前。","id":255},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"但是，你能不能睁大眼睛好好看看，现在是絮絮叨叨念叨过去的时候吗？","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"你不会杀死我，那我们就应当放下芥蒂，团结一致去面对火龙。","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"我仍信任你作为猎人的能力，如果可以，我也愿意把背后交给你。","id":258},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#4$1","id":259},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"后面不要再为这种事浪费时间。","id":260},{"type":"dialog","id":261},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1.5","id":262},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":263},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":264},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#5$1","id":265},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"不......你什么都不知道......","id":266,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"明，他是我的儿子......","id":267,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#7$1","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"他已经死了。","id":269,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e2/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":270},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#9$1","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"......","id":272},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"七年前的今天，也是这样的晚上，山里到处都是那些畜生的嚎叫。","id":274,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"我说了让他不要去，那些家伙是他们自找的，可不管我拿多难听的话骂他，他只是反复地说......","id":275,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#5$1","id":276},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"“不，我是村里的猎人。”他就一直这样说啊，一直说啊，然后头也不回地冲了出去。","id":277,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#2$1","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"后来，我再见到他的时候，他已经连话都说不出口了。","id":279,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"你知道吗？要不是身边的衣物和装备，我甚至都认不出他来。","id":280,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"阳光照在他的身上，他的手却好冷。","id":281,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#5$1","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"我不明白啊，我的儿子，他为什么就变成这样了呢？","id":283,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#6$1","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"我看见了......泷居应......还有那些*东国粗口*混蛋的背影。","id":285,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"我就知道了，这些发生的时候他们就在那里，可他们什么也没做！就眼睁睁地看着......看着我的儿子......","id":286,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"怎么可能......你怎么可能理解我......","id":287,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b9/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_750_1#3$1","id":288},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"（矛尖颤抖得厉害，胳膊也是......）","id":289,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/83/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_750_1#6$1","id":290},{"type":"playsound","key":"$MH_nekolow","id":291},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"（手指正朝一个地方移动，那是......喵！）","id":292,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_750_1#6$1","id":293},{"type":"playsound","key":"$MH_nekoinjured","id":294},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"夜刀阁下小心！他要把矛射出来了喵！","id":295,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":296},{"type":"character","id":297},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_singleblunt","volume":"1","id":298},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":299},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":300},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_750_1#6$1","id":301},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":302},{"type":"jump","name":"middle","xpos":"100","times":"1","power":"250","fadetime":"0.4","isblock":"false","id":303},{"type":"playsound","key":"$MH_nekogood","volume":"1","id":304},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"喵嗷！老夫抓到矛了！","id":306,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c9/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":307},{"type":"character","id":308},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#4$1","id":309},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"放开！","id":310,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b4/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":311},{"type":"character","id":312},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":313},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":314},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.03","block":"true","id":315},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_broadswordblood","volume":"1","id":316},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":317},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":318},{"type":"stopmusic","id":319},{"type":"text","text":"我听见耳边尖锐的风声，血珠从细小的擦痕中渗出来，沿着耳廓滴落。","id":320},{"type":"text","text":"矛尖插在我的左脚前，一半深深地埋入地面。","id":321},{"type":"text","text":"当我转过身去时，看见了老人浑浊......而震动的双目。","id":322},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#9$1","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"——！","id":324},{"type":"dialog","id":325},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#4$1","id":326},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"怎么会......我怎么......","id":327,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b4/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#11$1","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"我没事，你冷静......","id":329},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#4$1","id":330},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":331},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"别过来！","id":332,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b4/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#5$1","id":333},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"不、不是我......变成这样是你们害的......","id":334,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_755_1#3$1","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"柏生义冈","text":"你！还有你！都是你们的错！","id":336,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_755_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":337},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":338},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1","id":339},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":340},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1029_Yato2_1#11$1","id":341},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"柏生先生，呃——","id":342},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"（痛苦的喘息）","id":343},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"哈，啊，这里怎么......是刚才火龙的那一击......","id":344},{"type":"dialog","id":345},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown1","volume":"1","id":346},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1","id":347},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":348},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_750_1#3$1","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"随从艾露猫","text":"夜刀阁下，你怎么倒下了？情况——","id":350,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/83/Avg_avg_npc_750_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"character","id":351},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜刀","text":"不用管我！随从艾露猫！去追上他！","id":352},{"type":"dialog","id":353},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":354},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":355},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":356},{"type":"character","id":357},{"type":"image","id":358}],"characters":["夜刀","柏生义冈","随从艾露猫","工匠猫"]}